{{italic title}}
The '''''American Architects Directory''''' is a directory of American architects registered with the [[American Institute of Architects]]. It was published by [[R.R. Bowker LLC]]. The first edition was published in 1956,<ref name=AAD1>''American Architects Directory'', First Edition ([[New York City]]: [[R.R. Bowker LLC]], 1956)</ref> second edition in 1962,<ref name=AAD2>''American Architects Directory'', Second Edition ([[New York City]]: [[R.R. Bowker LLC]], 1962)</ref> and third edition in 1970.<ref name=AAD3>''American Architects Directory'', Third Edition ([[New York City]]: [[R.R. Bowker LLC]], 1970).</ref>

== Links ==
http://public.aia.org/sites/hdoaa/wiki/Wiki%20Pages/1956%20American%20Architects%20Directory.aspx
http://public.aia.org/sites/hdoaa/wiki/Wiki%20Pages/1962%20American%20Architects%20Directory.aspx
http://public.aia.org/sites/hdoaa/wiki/Wiki%20Pages/1970%20American%20Architects%20Directory.aspx

