{{unref|date=January 2018}} The '''''Cartularium Saxonicum''''' is a three volume collection of Anglo-Saxon charters published from 1885 to 1893 by [[Walter de Gray Birch]] (1842-1924), then working in the Department of Manuscripts at the [[British Library]].
